Challenge: [Stop gninnipS My sdroW!](https://www.codewars.com/kata/5264d2b162488dc400000001/javascript)
Date Completed: July 17
Difficulty: 6 kyu
User Profile: https://www.codewars.com/users/andysantiagopr

Solution:
function spinWords(string){
  return string
    .split(" ") // Convert the sentence into an array of words
    .map(word => 
      word.length >= 5 
        ? word.split("").reverse().join("") // Reverse if word is 5+ characters
        : word
    )
    .join(" "); // Join the array back into a string
}

Examples:
spinWords("Hey fellow warriors") ➞ "Hey wollef sroirraw"
spinWords("This is a test") ➞ "This is a test"
spinWords("This is another test") ➞ "This is rehtona test"
*/
